teach them a lesson?

04:46.160 --> 04:49.580
T-Teach Rebel a lesson.
I meant, teach Rebel.

04:49.998 --> 04:51.833
I'm supposed to have
a date with her later.

04:51.916 --> 04:54.127
Wait, so you <i>are </i> still dating her?

04:54.210 --> 04:55.670
What happened to our plan,

04:55.753 --> 04:57.422
